				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ki%E1%BA%BFm-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-xUrU6GQqHJHqh6KK_laSXQ">Kiếm kỳ 1 - 劍其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-Jg_4_inbL47zGqzn3fJTrw">Lạc Thành Tương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Li%C3%AAm-Pha-bi/poem-i_NoAePnrwTzLj9rOA9C2w">Liêm Pha bi - 廉頗碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Nam-Ninh-ng%E1%BB%A5c/poem-rtTp4PUPw8zg7eBCEbPt6A">Nam Ninh ngục - 南寧獄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/%C3%94-sinh/poem-oq6-1foKgMOW5Y2FSvnWOw">Ô sinh - 烏生</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Lan-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C3%A0i-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-_0kVqenJGRyi535nuJrk6g">Sài Sơn tự - 柴山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Lan-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-nd0Dc2rDm_CVSYltcv5irQ">Lan Hương thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-038/poem-nOwfWuy9RGWc72TqXucE-A">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 038 - 山居百詠其三十八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/S%C6%B0-T%E1%BB%AD-l%C3%A2m-ca/poem-2aJCr5A9EBy5oBgi4_5IIg">Sư Tử lâm ca - 獅子林歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/author-leXS2a46kBYHa9AoDh5zfw">Ngô Tích Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-T%E1%BB%B1-Tr%C3%A2n/T%C3%A2y-giao-l%E1%BA%A1c-hoa-ca/poem-jyO0RzeP5_bTHpqrU9OhkQ">Tây giao lạc hoa ca - 西郊落花歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-T%E1%BB%B1-Tr%C3%A2n/author-7r72VrPQwdDMRtQY4fV6gg">Cung Tự Trân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu-T%E1%BA%ADp/T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n-chi-Ki%E1%BA%BFm-C%C3%A1c-th%E1%BB%91i/poem-Vq0BVNQe-V1of6SaEfjW-g">Tống nhân chi Kiếm Các thối - 送人之劍閣倅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu-T%E1%BA%ADp/author-mIUafUHZa2BMhE3Gz4w1gw">Ngu Tập</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-%C3%8Dch-K%C3%ADnh/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BB%87nh-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-l%E1%BA%A1c-hoa-h%C3%AD-th%C3%A0nh/poem-JggMoCgHDIicIh3ir5iYFQ">Xuân nhật bệnh trung đối lạc hoa hí thành - 春日病中對落花戲成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-%C3%8Dch-K%C3%ADnh/author-cLBAr9NBgdNtXR4eTFi7Ng">Diêu Ích Kính</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
